Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:09.06,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that I'll never forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:20.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,We once lived in a hopelessly sweet, miraculous time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:44.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The name of that brilliant time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:53.32,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:55.43,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
