Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:05.29,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:10.83,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.46,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:22.32,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:28.28,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:30.56,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:34.75,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:40.10,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:45.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:52.31,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.57,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:58.16,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:04.30,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:06.49,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:16.79,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:27.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:37.85,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Our time together started in an apartment building...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:41.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...that was relatively close to school but left behind by the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.65,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Back then, unable to find my way in life, I was drifting about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:56.74,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...even though I had entered an art college.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Yo, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:04.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I bought bentos for us at the convenience store, so let's eat them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:06.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:08.64,clover,,0,0,0,,What? Food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Do you have mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll eat anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.59,clover,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing, Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.02,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't care! Gimme the chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:25.30,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But those ordinary days with the people I love were also enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:26.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Nice, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:29.64,thoughts,,0,0,0,,They were fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.21,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And during that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.62,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I met you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.42,thoughts,,0,0,0,,My love for you began back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure it was the same for Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:09.37,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But we weren't the only ones who had begun to revolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.75,clover,,0,0,0,,You still haven't gotten over her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:27.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Actually, how many more girls will have to cry for you to be satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:27.09,crowd,,0,0,0,,Yamada! Yamada! Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Why is it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.85,clover,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you blow steam at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.07,clover,,0,0,0,,I probably won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:40.56,clover,,0,0,0,,You're better off finding another guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.99,clover,,0,0,0,,You should stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll be there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:02.55,clover,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.14,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.35,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Mayama-san's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.68,clover,,0,0,0,,It was a terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:25.31,clover,,0,0,0,,If a passing truck driver hadn't pulled Rika out, she would've burned up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika was the one driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:40.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Because of that event, I lost my best friend and Rika's husband at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Grab on tight. You'll fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:01.49,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamada... Why did you fall in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.42,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You're precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:11.06,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So, I've been thinking that I needed to turn you down properly if you ever told me that you liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:17.28,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But... I thought that you'd go away somewhere if I turned you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:22.99,thoughts,,0,0,0,,When I looked at you, it hurt me because it was like looking at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:28.65,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I thought, "Ah, I wonder if I look like that from Rika-san's perspective..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.94,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Uncool and persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.89,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.47,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Even thought I tried to act cool, I couldn't change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And I'm still uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:47.30,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't able to give up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada, did you just drool on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.13,clover,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.37,clover,,0,0,0,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:05.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:06.53,clover,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:12.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.74,clover,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.26,clover,,0,0,0,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:18.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.81,clover,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:32.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Is H-Hagu f-f-friends with Morita now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:38.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know how Hagu-chan feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.69,clover,,0,0,0,,But Morita-san probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:43.32,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Sensei, please don't ask me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you... not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back, Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Were you able to buy what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Did Morita leave already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.95,clover,,0,0,0,,W-Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.87,clover,,0,0,0,,It wasn't fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.00,clover,,0,0,0,,It wasn't fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.67,clover,,0,0,0,,It was hard to keep up with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.71,clover,,0,0,0,,...and my f-feet hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:38.38,clover,,0,0,0,,And when I wanted to go to the restroom, I couldn't tell him for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:39.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:43.79,clover,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even remember what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.37,clover,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:54.35,clover,,0,0,0,,I mean, the whole time, I wanted to come back as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.95,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.66,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd much rather be with you, Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.35,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd like it much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:07.95,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You're so naive... it's obviously because you like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.11,clover,,0,0,0,,I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Why you, Hagusuke, Chibi-Hamus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.33,clover,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Have you been well? Yeah? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.62,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it? Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Want some sunflower seeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.03,clover,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.67,clover,,0,0,0,,It's kinda cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.00,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Look! A rolled mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:24.45,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Even so, why is it, Morita-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.36,clover,,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.60,clover,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:43.04,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't get it! Why are you always being so selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.38,clover,,0,0,0,,You'll lose all of them like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:49.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:53.38,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Morita-san left for America...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:58.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan, do you want Morita-san to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Or do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.93,clover,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Takemoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, what good will asking her that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.58,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.24,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:17.27,clover,,0,0,0,,I think it's good to keep trying until you've tried everything you've wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:24.50,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Morita-san left for America, and Hagu-chan continued to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.05,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't able to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:45.24,thoughts,,0,0,0,,After graduating from college, Mayama-san started working for a design company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.82,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And love was slowly starting to revolve there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:53.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:59.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Remember that bowl that you made at your school for the restaurant on Omote-Sandou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:04.21,clover,,0,0,0,,We've had other customers order that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:05.91,clover,,0,0,0,,They want "something similar".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:12.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Not really, I had a friend of mine make that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:17.05,clover,,0,0,0,,There are things I want to ask her to make as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.36,clover,,0,0,0,,Can you introduce me to this Yamada-san next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.11,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll ask her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.97,clover,,0,0,0,,But I'll have to talk to her about money...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.39,clover,,0,0,0,,The specifications are more detailed this time around. I should talk to her in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:33.56,clover,,0,0,0,,It'll be no problem as long as you give me the budget report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Please leave the rest up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:43.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:48.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.22,clover,,0,0,0,,My name is Nomiya. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that bowl the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.33,clover,,0,0,0,,It was well-received.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.08,clover,,0,0,0,,You really helped us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.94,thoughts,,0,0,0,,He's a cool-looking guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.91,clover,,0,0,0,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:16.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Why are you interfering with us when you're interested in someone else, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:24.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san's feelings for you are obvious to even us, so there's no way you haven't noticed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:30.07,clover,,0,0,0,,And you're not pushing her away, but rather, you're tormenting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:39.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's that you want to keep her "on the bench", in case your first choice doesn't work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.48,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:51.31,clover,,0,0,0,,"I'll take the unspoiled Yamada-san if Rika-san doesn't work out."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Thinking something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:55.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.20,clover,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.21,clover,,0,0,0,,You said that you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.26,clover,,0,0,0,,We're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.76,clover,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:20.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:30.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada... Nomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.22,clover,,0,0,0,,You know about Rika-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:43.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you just waiting for them to fall apart while you complain and sulk, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.65,clover,,0,0,0,,P-Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.47,clover,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you, Nomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:48.62,clover,,0,0,0,,It doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though you used me to attract Mayama's attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:56.05,clover,,0,0,0,,You're sure being selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.38,clover,,0,0,0,,How much longer will you keep testing Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I do understand your position...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:05.24,clover,,0,0,0,,An unrequited love that's emerged is unproductive, but simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Your infatuation makes him feel guilty, so he's nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.67,clover,,0,0,0,,And nothing worse could possibly happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Nor will you be hurt anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:23.60,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it about Mayama that you like, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.11,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:31.88,clover,,0,0,0,,If my love for him is genuine, I should be able to wish for his happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:37.34,clover,,0,0,0,,But I... Just like you said in the car earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:42.16,clover,,0,0,0,,I had honestly... been hoping they'd fall apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.80,clover,,0,0,0,,This whole time... this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Please have some while it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.14,clover,,0,0,0,,Why, Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you when I left this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.74,clover,,0,0,0,,That I'll come back, even if you're not waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:13.46,clover,,0,0,0,,I already said this at the hospital, but I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:16.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Please employ me at Harada Design.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:20.05,clover,,0,0,0,,I should be more useful than I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.00,clover,,0,0,0,,The same thing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.85,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll end up hurting you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.84,clover,,0,0,0,,It's okay, you can hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Because I won't be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:40.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I hadn't realized what had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.01,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...since I was too absorbed in my own matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:51.29,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And that didn't change at all, even when Morita-san came back from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.36,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm... incapable of doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I started pedaling without a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.94,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...without even knowing the meaning behind my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:22.03,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I was afraid this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.10,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of not knowing the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of not knowing what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:34.13,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of myself for not knowing what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:42.45,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And I was afraid of the days that were nevertheless flying by mercilessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:58.40,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}itsumo nakayoshi de ii yo ne tte iwarete\NEven when I'm told, "It's so nice that you two get along so well..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:03.76,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}demo dokoka blue ni natteta\NBut I was feeling blue somewhere inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:05.74,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnMatura MT Script Capitals\fs48\c&HE0D3CA&\3c&H5F514D&\pos(358,330)}Northernmost Point in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:06.36,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}are wa koi datta\NThat was love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:10.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,This is the end of Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:11.95,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nando mo kuchi no naka tsubuyaitemita\NI tried whispering it to myself many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:19.73,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kasukana image dake wo oimotometeta\N...while I was pursuing that faint image.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:24.71,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}toki wa koborete iku yo\NTime will fly by...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:34.41,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chachi na yume no sekai mo sugu ni hirogatte iku yo\N...and my simple dream world will quickly expand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:39.61,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi wa iroasenu mama\N...but you'll stay vivid in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:45.41,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}warufuzake de tobeta no sa\NI was able to fly when I was messing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:58.67,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ki no sei da to satorazu ni irareta nara\NIf only I hadn't realized that I imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:04.40,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sandal-baki no ashiyubi ni mitoreta\NI was charmed by your toes in your sandals...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Always... I'd always thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:09.27,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chiisana hana sakaseta\N...while we tended to that small flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:10.30,thoughts,,0,0,0,,"How far can I go without looking back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.40,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}are wa koi datta\NThat was love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:15.70,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That was the reason I started riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:20.00,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I finally understood that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:30.64,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}toki wa koborete iku yo\NTime will fly by...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:35.15,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I probably wanted to distance myself from everyone, so I could understand how important they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:40.40,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chachi na yume no sekai mo sugu ni hirogatte iku yo\N...and my simple dream world will quickly expand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.55,thoughts,,0,0,0,,How precious they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:45.46,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi wa iroasenu mama\N...but you'll stay vivid in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.35,clover,,0,0,0,,What was the end of this land like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:51.42,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ameagari no kirema kara\NShining through between the clouds after the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.58,clover,,0,0,0,,There was nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.10,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:20:03.99,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sashikomu hi no hikaritachi machi wo arau\NThe rays of sunshine bathe the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:55.78,clover,,0,0,0,,...it was bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.43,clover,,0,0,0,,The sky was so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.99,clover,,0,0,0,,...it made me want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.85,clover,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:10.40,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}itsumo nakayoshi de ii yo ne tte iwarete\NEven when I'm told, "It's so nice that you two get along so well..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:15.77,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}demo dokoka blue ni natteta\NBut I was feeling blue somewhere inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:19.17,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}are wa koi datta\NThat was love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.85,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:45.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun, thank you for coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.89,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:55.20,thoughts,,0,0,0,,We all start to revolve again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.79,thoughts,,0,0,0,,We start to revolve again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:29.80,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:29.80,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:40.26,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:40.26,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.68,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.68,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:52.81,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:52.81,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:22:06.29,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:22:06.29,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:09.03,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:09.03,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.89,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.89,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.23,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.23,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:24.93,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:24.93,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:28.33,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:28.33,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:34.13,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Unable to say what you want...
